## FILE STRUCTURE

```
/app
  /(store)/              ← customer-facing pages
    page.tsx             ← landing
    shop/page.tsx        ← product catalog
    order/success/       ← post-checkout confirmation
  /(studio)/             ← design editor
    studio/page.tsx      ← main canvas page
    studio/mockups/      ← mockup review + checkout entry
  /api/
    designs/save/        ← save canvas state
    designs/upload-file/ ← upload design PNG → Supabase + Printful
    printful/
      catalog/           ← get enabled products
      variants/[id]/     ← get product variants
      mockup-task/       ← create mockup task
      mockup-task/[id]/  ← poll mockup status
    checkout/
      create-session/    ← Stripe checkout session creation
    webhooks/
      stripe/            ← payment events (creates Printful order)
      printful/          ← mockup + fulfillment events
/components
  /studio/               ← Fabric.js canvas components
    PlacementSelector    ← which print areas to use
    PlacementTabs        ← tab per placement
    DesignCanvas         ← Fabric.js wrapper
    DesignToolbar        ← text/image/undo tools
  /shop/                 ← product browsing
  /ui/                   ← shared components
/hooks
  useDesignSession.ts    ← manages all session state
/lib
  /config/
    products.config.ts   ← SINGLE SOURCE for products/placements/pricing
  /printful/
    client.ts            ← server-only Printful v2 API client
    types.ts             ← Printful TypeScript types
  /supabase/
    client.ts            ← browser client (anon key)
    server.ts            ← server client (service role)
/docs
  goldengoosetees-knowledge.md     ← MASTER knowledge doc
  ggt-multi-placement-addendum.md  ← placement flow
  printful-console-setup.md        ← Printful token setup guide
/supabase
  migrations/            ← SQL migration files
/scripts
  seed-products.ts       ← populate products_catalog from Printful
api/
  _lib/                  ← shared serverless helpers (DO NOT DELETE)
```

---

## API ROUTE RESPONSE CONTRACT

All API routes return one of:
```typescript
// Success
{ success: true, data: T }

// Error
{ success: false, error: string, code: string }
```

No exceptions. No other shapes. Every route has try/catch. Every catch logs via console.error.

---

## DATABASE TABLES (Supabase PostgreSQL)

### designs
```
id, user_id (nullable), session_id, status,
selected_product_id (printful catalog_product_id),
selected_variant_ids (integer[]),
selected_placements (text[]),
canvas_data (jsonb: { "front": fabricjs_json, "back": fabricjs_json }),
placement_file_urls (jsonb: { "front": "https://...", "back": "..." }),
placement_file_ids (jsonb: { "front": "pf_id_abc", "back": "pf_id_xyz" }),
mockup_task_ids (jsonb: { "combined": 12345 }),
mockup_results (jsonb: { "front": [{variant_id, mockup_url}], "back": [...] }),
mockup_status (text: pending|partial|complete|failed),
created_at, updated_at
```

### orders
```
id, user_id (nullable), session_id, design_id,
stripe_payment_intent_id, stripe_session_id,
printful_order_id, status (pending_payment|paid|submitted|fulfilled|shipped),
shipping_address (jsonb), line_items (jsonb),
retail_amount, printful_cost, created_at, updated_at
```

### products_catalog (local Printful cache)
```
printful_product_id (PK), title, type, thumbnail_url,
variants (jsonb), placements (jsonb), is_active, updated_at
```

