## CANVAS EXPORT SPECIFICATIONS

- Display size: 800×800px
- Export size: placement.canvasExportPx (from ProductConfig.placements[])
  - Standard apparel front/back: 1800×1800px minimum (150 DPI @ 12"×12")
  - Sleeves: 525×525px (150 DPI @ 3.5"×3.5")
  - Mug wrap: 1275×525px (150 DPI @ 8.5"×3.5")
- Format: PNG with transparency
- Method: canvas.setDimensions({width: exportPx, height: exportPx}) → toDataURL → restore

---

## RATE LIMIT HANDLING (Printful)

Printful v2 uses token bucket: 120 req/min general; lower for mockup endpoints.
Headers: X-Ratelimit-Remaining, X-Ratelimit-Reset
On 429: wait X-Ratelimit-Reset seconds, retry (max 3 attempts, exponential backoff).
NEVER fire-and-forget Printful requests without handling 429.

