## COMMON BUGS TO WATCH FOR

1. Using v1 Printful endpoints → switch to v2
2. Awaiting mockup results synchronously → must be async/webhook/poll
3. Re-uploading design files on every action → reuse placement_file_ids
4. Creating Printful orders on success page → must be in Stripe webhook handler
5. Stripe webhook using req.json() → must use req.text() raw body
6. Hardcoded product/variant IDs → load from products.config.ts or DB
7. Client component importing PRINTFUL_API_KEY → server route only
8. Missing 429 handling on Printful calls → exponential backoff required
9. Anonymous session designs not migrating on auth → must run in auth callback
10. Canvas exported at display size (800px) → must export at canvasExportPx

---

## FORBIDDEN PATTERNS (THESE ARE BUGS)

```typescript
// ❌ WRONG — v1 endpoint
fetch('https://api.printful.com/mockup-generator/tasks', ...)

// ❌ WRONG — awaiting mockup synchronously
const mockup = await createMockupTask(...)  // task_id only, not images!

// ❌ WRONG — Printful call in component
const products = await fetch('/printful/products')  // use /api/ proxy

// ❌ WRONG — creating order from success page
// app/(store)/order/success/page.tsx
await printful.post('/v2/orders', ...)  // NEVER HERE

// ❌ WRONG — hardcoded variant ID
const variantId = 4011  // load from DB

// ❌ WRONG — client price
const price = searchParams.get('price')  // calculate server-side

// ❌ WRONG — Stripe webhook body parsing
const body = await req.json()  // breaks signature verification; use req.text()
```

